**Finding:** No security-related HTTP headers are set. Responses lack `Content-Security-Policy`, `X-Content-Type-Options`, `X-Frame-Options`, `Strict-Transport-Security`, etc.

**Risk:** OWASP A05 – Security Misconfiguration

**Fix:** Add `helmet` (one line):

